Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:15.02,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,{All right!}Được rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.94,Bullet_Main,lady,0,0,0,,{So you must be Enju-chan.}Em chắc là Enju-chan nhỉ?
