Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:26.17,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,{It's...}Đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:28.72,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,{Miori's blood.}máu của Miori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.51,Bullet_Main,lady,0,0,0,,{You're not going to back down, are you?}Cậu sẽ không định lùi bước phải không nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.10,Bullet_Main,both,0,0,0,,Bắt đầu rồi.{There we go.}
